casebody.head_matter:
Patricia A. DILTS, et vir, petitioners,
v.
COLD SPRING FOREST SECTION 1 HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION, INC., et al.
No. 13-6788.
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 9, 2013.
Motion of petitioners for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioners allowed until December 30, 2013, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
